metadata.name: Cat teasing stick
metadata.description:
She is the magic girl of cat toys  
Magic wand is the Cat teasing stick  
Occasional long-range attacks with cat dewormer

Her day job is to play with the cats  
Keeping the cats healthy  
What's a little heartbreaking is that  
She has cat scratches all over her body  
So she has to put a lot of band-aids on her body

Even so, she loves her job the most!
